gujarati.context:
Here are the translations:

From now on, not you, but God will take care of you; 
He will show me my own account with His; 
I spoke thus, I was silent as stone, then destiny wrote its fate.

Here is the translation:

Hare fare kare kaani kaam, Nide Satsangi ne aathun jaam;
Em karataan Viitya kaani dan, Pachhi Bolyo thainene Prasanna.
